{
  "stem": "17625.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- [LAUGHS] and I-- this is the way it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He worked in-- in leather manufacturing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The work?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He opened up shop, and he made parts of shoes, the-- the soft parts of shoes, which at the time, whoever assembled shoes, he bought the-- the soft part already made.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whatever they had, they made the soles, they put in the soles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they finished the shoe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was his-- this was his profession.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- he sold it to-- to-- to-- not to shop, to customers, which, they made the shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in Chrzanow, [SIGHS] most part in Chrzanow till the-- in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he opened up shop in Cracow, which was wholesale leather, just leather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Chrzanow later, he gave up also the parts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he just sold leather to the leather trade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which other words-- the other ones who made the parts, and the other ones who made the shoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They bought leather, just leather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was for his profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, when my brother-- which is now in Belgium, the older brother of me, with-- with him, he put my brother-- in-- in Cracow, he opened up a wholesale place in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Avraham Shmiel Fuchsbrunner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mindl Tauber.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mindl Tauber.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother had-- had a profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she had a shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She made shirts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She made-- she made ladies' wears.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I was the youngest in the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I [SIGHS] was a kid, she was well-established.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she didn't work no more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But before, when she was single, maybe-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe she had one kid, two kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She still worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then she gave it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't need it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My older sister, Golda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Golda Lya.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then came my brother, Bendit.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
